                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><encodingDesc><tagsDecl>&amp;renditions;</tagsDecl></encodingDesc></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_bællæx" xml:lang="os"><form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>bællæx</orth></form><form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>bællax</orth></form><sense><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>беда</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>misfortune</q></tr></sense><exampleGrp><example><quote>styr bællæxtæ jyl sæmbældī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>его постигли большие несчастья</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>big misfortune came to him</q></tr></example><example><quote>cydær bællæx ærxæstæg kæny</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>приближается какая-то беда</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>some bad luck is coming</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Брит."/><biblScope>108</biblScope></bibl></example><example xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg><lang/></usg><quote>ke bællaxæj næ baxumæ kodta skʼola?</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>по чьей вине („беде“) не произвела вспашки школа?</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>whose fault (“misfortune”) was the fact that the school did not make ploughing?</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_SD"/><biblScope>273%l2%l</biblScope></bibl></example><example xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg><lang/></usg><quote>razamundi bællaxæj næ jes kust</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>из-за недостатка („беды“) руководства не ведется работы</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>the work is not in progress due to the weakness (“misfortune”) of the direction</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_SD"/><biblScope>246%l3%l</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><exampleGrp><example><quote>styr bællæxtæ jyl sæmbældī</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>его постигли большие несчастья</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>big misfortune came to him</q></tr></example><example><quote>cydær bællæx ærxæstæg kæny</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>приближается какая-то беда</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>some bad luck is coming</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Брит."/><biblScope>108</biblScope></bibl></example><example xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg><lang/></usg><quote>ke bællaxæj næ baxumæ kodta skʼola?</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>по чьей вине („беде“) не произвела вспашки школа?</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>whose fault (“misfortune”) was the fact that the school did not make ploughing?</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_SD"/><biblScope>273%l2%l</biblScope></bibl></example><example xml:lang="os-x-digor"><usg><lang/></usg><quote>razamundi bællaxæj næ jes kust</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>из-за недостатка („беды“) руководства не ведется работы</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>the work is not in progress due to the weakness (“misfortune”) of the direction</q></tr><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_SD"/><biblScope>246%l3%l</biblScope></bibl></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang=""><lang/> <w>balā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="tr"><lang/> <w>bala</w> <gloss><q>беда</q></gloss></mentioned>. Распространено у всех кавказских народов мусульманской культуры: <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/> <w>balæ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ce"><lang/> <w>bala</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/> <w>baláh</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lbe"><lang/> <w>balā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="dar"><lang/> <w>balá</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/> <w>balá</w></mentioned> и др. Конечное -%iх%i находит поддержку в <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/> <w>baláh</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/> <w>balah</w></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang=""><lang/> <w>balā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="tr"><lang/> <w>bala</w> <gloss><q>misfortune</q></gloss></mentioned>. The word is widespread through all Caucasian people of Islamic culture: <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/> <w>balæ</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="ce"><lang/> <w>bala</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/> <w>baláh</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lbe"><lang/> <w>balā</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="dar"><lang/> <w>balá</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="lez"><lang/> <w>balá</w></mentioned> etc. The final -%iх%i is found in <mentioned xml:lang="av"><lang/> <w>baláh</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="krc-x-balkar"><lang/> <w>balah</w></mentioned>.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>